title: Liz Cheney: Midterm Results Were a ‘Clear Victory for Team Normal’
description: Ms. Cheney, who lost her Republican House primary in August to a Trump-backed rival, said that the midterm election results were a rejection of the former president.
dc:creator: Neil Vigdor
category: House Select Committee to Investigate the January 6th Attack
media:credit: Emily Elconin for The New York Times
media:description: Representative Liz Cheney of Wyoming was one of 10 House Republicans who voted for former President Donald J. Trump’s impeachment in 2021.
